</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F2C56F1D-ACED-4AF2-AF6A-6F4895B469BA" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Partial Commit Allowed by Customer
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-12B1A1EA-8CBD-4687-8158-F9256D83E505" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>B2B Channel: Order changes may go on HOLD automatically for review based on validation matrix (RICEFW) as applicable. There will be no automatic rejection​

Special Check with Finance (Manual) is done for cross-quarter ​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-521D018B-DED1-47AB-9045-DA440F87E48D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Change in following fields will result for the Order Change. Change tracking will be enabled via standard SAP functionality so that any order changes can be logged for later review.​

Quantity Change​

Price change​

Requested Delivery date change​

NCNR flag  and Cancellation window during  sales Order changes for Intel Foundry will be manual.​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2DAC9B17-DC37-4143-9999-4C2DCF9E5B4C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
