      <textAnnotation id="sid-10706610-3EEE-473F-812D-3BC692561BE0" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Financial Posting will be replicated realtime from individual S4 box to CFIN system
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-77221AA8-262E-46C4-9755-19B2C99777F1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1) Manual Channel  - CBA will due diligence outside SAP and once approved only, it will be accepted into SAP without any hold.​

2) Capture Approved change in order &amp; ​

Acknowledgement if it is via manual channel​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
